<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Theia Aurora — Handmade by Saira</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Jost:wght@200;300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
  --ink: #4a2f2f;
  --parchment: #f7f2eb;
  --gold: #f3b6c8;
  --gold-light: #f8d6df;
  --warm-dark: #5a3838;
  --muted: #9b7474;
  --cream: #faf6f0;
}

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  header {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    padding: 20px 48px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    background: rgba(250, 246, 240, 0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.2);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .logo {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; line-height: 1;
  }
  .logo-main {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .logo-sub {
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  nav { display: flex; gap: 36px; align-items: center; }
  nav a {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  nav a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    padding-top: 80px;
  }

  .hero-text {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
    padding: 80px 64px 80px 80px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .hero-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 380px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 14px 40px;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--parchment);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .hero-image {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--warm-dark);
  }
  .hero-image img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    opacity: 0.9;
    transition: transform 8s ease;
  }
  .hero-image:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }

  .hero-ornament {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 48px; left: 64px;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.6);
  }

  /* ── MARQUEE ── */
  .marquee-bar {
    background: var(--ink);
    padding: 14px 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .marquee-inner {
    display: inline-block;
    animation: marquee 20s linear infinite;
  }
  .marquee-inner span {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin: 0 40px;
  }
  .marquee-inner span.dot {
    color: rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.4);
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }
  @keyframes marquee {
    0% { transform: translateX(0); }
    100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
  }

  /* ── SECTION HEADERS ── */
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 80px 40px 60px;
  }
  .section-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .section-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }
  .section-rule {
    width: 48px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    margin: 24px auto 0;
  }

  /* ── COLLECTION GRID ── */
  .collection {
    padding: 0 40px 100px;
  }
  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    max-width: 1300px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .card {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--warm-dark);
    cursor: pointer;
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
  }
  .card img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: transform 0.7s ease, opacity 0.4s ease;
    opacity: 0.88;
  }
  .card:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.06);
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .card-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(26,20,16,0.85) 0%, rgba(26,20,16,0.1) 50%, transparent 100%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 32px 28px;
    opacity: 1;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
  }

  .card-name {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .card-tagline {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
    opacity: 0;
  }
  .card:hover .card-tagline {
    max-height: 80px;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .card-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.4);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    transform: translateY(10px);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: all 0.3s ease 0.1s;
  }
  .card:hover .card-cta {
    transform: translateY(0);
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .card-emoji {
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px; right: 20px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  /* ── MODAL ── */
  .modal-overlay {
    display: none;
    position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 200;
    background: rgba(26,20,16,0.7);
    backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 24px;
  }
  .modal-overlay.open { display: flex; }

  .modal {
    background: var(--cream);
    max-width: 900px; width: 100%;
    max-height: 90vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  }

  .modal-img { overflow: hidden; }
  .modal-img img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .modal-body {
    padding: 56px 48px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .modal-close {
    position: absolute; top: 20px; right: 24px;
    background: none; border: none;
    font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--muted);
    cursor: pointer;
    line-height: 1;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .modal-close:hover { color: var(--ink); }

  .modal-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .modal-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .modal-rule { width: 36px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 24px; }

  .modal-desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .modal-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    border: 1px solid rgba(138,125,110,0.35);
    padding: 6px 14px;
    margin-right: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .modal-inquire {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 28px;
    padding: 13px 36px;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--parchment);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }
  .modal-inquire:hover { background: transparent; color: var(--ink); }

  /* ── ABOUT ── */
  .about {
  background: #B76F7C;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  min-height: 60vh;
}

  .about-box {
  padding: 70px 34px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  border-right: 1px solid rgba(247,242,235,0.25);
}

.about-box:nth-child(1) {
  background: #B76F7C;
}

.about-box:nth-child(2) {
  background: #C98293;
}

.about-box:nth-child(3) {
  background: #D8A2A9;
}

.about-box:nth-child(4) {
  background: #EFD1D5;
}

.about-box:nth-child(1) .about-eyebrow,
.about-box:nth-child(1) .about-title,
.about-box:nth-child(1) .about-body,
.about-box:nth-child(2) .about-eyebrow,
.about-box:nth-child(2) .about-title,
.about-box:nth-child(2) .about-body {
  color: #FFF3F5;
}

.about-box:nth-child(3) .about-eyebrow,
.about-box:nth-child(3) .about-title,
.about-box:nth-child(3) .about-body {
  color: #5A3038;
}

.about-box:nth-child(4) .about-eyebrow,
.about-box:nth-child(4) .about-title,
.about-box:nth-child(4) .about-body {
  color: #4A252D;
}

.about-box:nth-child(1) .about-title em,
.about-box:nth-child(2) .about-title em {
  color: #FFF3F5;
}

.about-box:nth-child(3) .about-title em,
.about-box:nth-child(4) .about-title em {
  color: #4A252D;
}

.about-box:last-child {
  border-right: none;
}

.about-box .about-body + .about-body {
  margin-top: 18px;
}

  .about-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--parchment);
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .about-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }

  .about-body {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.95;
    color: rgba(247,242,235,0.6);
    max-width: 400px;
  }

  .about-visual {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D8A2A9 0%, #EFD1D5 100%);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-monogram {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 14rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(201,169,110,0.08);
    line-height: 1;
    user-select: none;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
  }

  .about-badge {
    position: absolute;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .about-badge small {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(201,169,110,0.5);
    font-style: normal;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  /* ── CONTACT ── */
  .contact {
    padding: 100px 40px;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--parchment);
  }

  .contact-inner { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .contact p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .contact-links { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .contact-link {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(26,20,16,0.25);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .contact-link:hover { background: var(--ink); color: var(--parchment); }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: var(--ink);
    padding: 36px 48px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px;
  }

  .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--parchment);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .footer-copy {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: rgba(247,242,235,0.35);
  }

  .footer-saira {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-style: italic;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    header { padding: 16px 24px; }
    nav { gap: 20px; }
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-image { min-height: 50vh; }
    .hero-text { padding: 60px 32px; }
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .about { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-visual { min-height: 300px; }
    .modal { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .modal-img { max-height: 50vh; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    header { padding: 14px 20px; }
    nav a { display: none; }
    nav a:last-child { display: block; }
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-title { font-size: 2.5rem; }
    .collection { padding: 0 0 60px; }
    .about-text { padding: 60px 32px; }
    .contact { padding: 60px 24px; }
    footer { padding: 28px 24px; }
    .modal-body { padding: 36px 28px; }
  }

  /* ── FADE IN ── */
  .fade-in {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(24px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }
  .fade-in.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header>
  <a href="#" class="logo" style="text-decoration:none;">
    <span class="logo-main">Theia Aurora</span>
    <span class="logo-sub">Handmade by Saira</span>
  </a>
  <nav>
    <a href="#collection">Collection</a>
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-text">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">✦ Handcrafted Beadwork Jewelry</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Worn with<br><em>intention,</em><br>made with love.</h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">Each piece from Theia Aurora is woven bead by bead — a quiet labor of love that carries its own story, texture, and soul.</p>
    <a href="#collection" class="btn-primary">Explore the Collection</a>
    <span class="hero-ornament">✦ Theia Aurora — Handmade by Saira</span>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-image">
    <img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" 
         id="hero-bg" alt="Theia Aurora jewelry" style="background:#2c2018;">
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MARQUEE -->
<div class="marquee-bar">
  <div class="marquee-inner" id="marquee">
    <span>Handmade by Saira</span><span class="dot">·</span>
    <span>Beaded with Love</span><span class="dot">·</span>
    <span>Theia Aurora</span><span class="dot">·</span>
    <span>Each Piece One of a Kind</span><span class="dot">·</span>
    <span>Crafted with Intention</span><span class="dot">·</span>
    <span>Handmade by Saira</span><span class="dot">·</span>
    <span>Beaded with Love</span><span class="dot">·</span>
    <span>Theia Aurora</span><span class="dot">·</span>
    <span>Each Piece One of a Kind</span><span class="dot">·</span>
    <span>Crafted with Intention</span><span class="dot">·</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- COLLECTION -->
<section id="collection">
  <div class="section-header fade-in">
    <p class="section-eyebrow">✦ The Collection</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">A collection of<br><em>handmade stories</em></h2>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="collection">
    <div class="grid" id="product-grid"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about-box fade-in">
    <p class="about-eyebrow">✦ A Personal Touch</p>
    <h2 class="about-title">Made to be<br><em>cherished.</em></h2>
    <p class="about-body">
      Choosing a handmade piece is an intimate experience. It's about more than just acquiring a product; it's about connecting with the creator and appreciating the time and effort that goes into each item. Our creations are designed to be cherished, serving as a reminder of the love and care that went into making them.
    </p>
    <p class="about-body">
      By opting for a handmade piece, you're supporting artisans and valuing the art of craftsmanship. We invite you to explore our collection and discover the unique beauty that each piece holds.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-box fade-in">
    <p class="about-eyebrow">✦ Made to Order</p>
    <h2 class="about-title">Created just<br><em>for you.</em></h2>
    <p class="about-body">
      Every piece is lovingly crafted to order, ensuring that your item is unique and tailored to your preferences. This process allows for a personal touch that simply cannot be achieved with machine-made goods. Our artisans pour their heart and soul into each creation, making it a small act of devotion.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-box fade-in">
    <p class="about-eyebrow">✦ The Beauty of Variability</p>
    <h2 class="about-title">No two pieces<br><em>are the same.</em></h2>
    <p class="about-body">
      One of the many charms of handmade items is their variability. While we strive for consistency, slight color variations may occur. This is not a flaw, but rather a reflection of the natural materials and processes we use, which add character and individuality to each piece.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-box fade-in">
    <p class="about-eyebrow">✦ Custom Color Requests</p>
    <h2 class="about-title">Your vision,<br><em>handmade.</em></h2>
    <p class="about-body">
      We understand that personal taste varies, and we welcome custom color requests. Our artisans are more than happy to work with you to bring your vision to life. Whether you're looking for a particular shade to match your decor or a color that holds special meaning to you, we are here to help.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CONTACT -->
<section class="contact" id="contact">
  <div class="contact-inner fade-in">
    <div class="section-header" style="padding: 0 0 40px;">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">✦ Get in Touch</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Inquire or<br><em>commission</em> a piece</h2>
      <div class="section-rule"></div>
    </div>
    <p>Interested in a piece, a custom order, or simply want to say hello? Reach out — each inquiry is answered personally by Saira.</p>
    <div class="contact-links">
      <a class="contact-link" href="mailto:sairajacob2689@gmail.com">✉ Email</a>
      <a class="contact-link" href="https://www.instagram.com/theia.aurora/">⬡ Instagram</a>
      <a class="contact-link" href="https://wa.me/919895199052">⬡ WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer>
  <span class="footer-logo">Theia Aurora</span>
  <span class="footer-saira">Handmade by Saira</span>
  <span class="footer-copy">© 2025 Theia Aurora. All rights reserved.</span>
